author: Warhammer
description:
Darktide's new class Hive Scum is coming to Darktide December 2, 2025! 

The Hive Scum comes screaming from the depths of the hive, leaving destruction and mayhem as they decimate their enemies with dual-wielding pistols & explosives from afar. Up close they are equally lethal, fighting dirty and tearing through enemies with makeshift saws, crowbars and dual-wielded shivs. Their fighting prowess is further enhanced by toxins and signature customizable Stimm. 

Wishlist now
